               <msContents>
                  <summary>

                    Prayer of the Covenant, Ṣälotä Kidan, ጸሎተ፡ ኪዳን፡ (f<locus target="#78r">fol. 78r</locus>-86v); Prayer to Mary, “Guard me,” ዕቀብኒ (87r-94r) mentioning the owner Walatta Giyorgis several times; Colophon 94r: "My Lady, I finished your wish; and may the Mother of God encourage you to fulfill my wish" ; Calendar: Lists of Holy days of Saints and Feasts.</summary>

                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i1">
                    <locus from="1r" to="67v" facs="005">Fols 1r–67v</locus>
                    <title type="complete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT4668Prayer">Protective prayers
                                                  for the seven weekdays</title>
                    <textLang mainLang="gez">Gǝ‘ǝz</textLang>
                      <msItem xml:id="ms_i1.1"><locus from="1r" to="8v" facs="005">Fols 1r–8v</locus><title>For Monday</title><incipit xml:lang="gez">በስመ፡ አብ፡ <gap reason="omitted"/> ጸሎቱ፡ ለጴጥሮስ ዝ ውእቱ፡ ዘየዓቢ፡ እምሐዋርያቲሁ፡ ዘዘኃረዮ፡ ክርስቶስ፡ እምቅድመ፡ ኵሎሙ፡ ሐዋርያቲሁ፡ ለኢየሱስ፡ ክርስቶስ፡ ወልደ፡ እግዚአብሔር፡ ሕያው፡ ወጸውዖሙ፡ ለኵሎሙ፡ ሐዋርያቲሁ፡ ወነበረ፡ ምስሌሆሙ፡ ወባረኮሙ። ወይቤሎሙ፡ አንትሙ፡ አራዕየ። አንትሙ፡ አኃውየ፡</incipit></msItem>
                      <msItem xml:id="ms_i1.2"><locus from="9r" to="16v" facs="013">Fols 9r–16v</locus><title>For Tuesday</title><incipit xml:lang="gez">በስመ፡ አብ፡ <gap reason="omitted"/> ጸሎት፡ በእንተ፡ መልከ፡ ጼዴቅ፡ ወበእንተ፡ ጰራቅሊጦስ፡ መንፈሰ፡ ጽድቅ፡</incipit></msItem>
                      <msItem xml:id="ms_i1.3"><locus from="17r" to="28r" facs="021">Fols 17r–28r</locus><title>For Wednesday</title><incipit xml:lang="gez">በስመ፡ አብ፡ <gap reason="omitted"/> ጸሎተ፡ መድኃኒት፡ አስማተ፡ ኃይላት፡ ዘወረደ፡ እምሰማያት፡ ዘወሀቦ፡ ለቶማስ፡ ረድእ፡ ለዘክሮቱ፡ ይደሉ፡ ሰጊድ፡</incipit></msItem>
                      <msItem xml:id="ms_i1.4"><locus from="29r" to="34r" facs="033">Fols 29r–34r</locus><title>For Thursday</title><incipit xml:lang="gez">በስመ፡ አብ፡ <gap reason="omitted"/> ለነ፡ ለሐዋርያት፡ ወሀበነ፡ ዘንተ፡ አስማተ፡ በደብረ፡ ዘይት፡ ወምስሌነ፡ እሙ፡ አመ፡ ዕለተ፡ እርገቱ፡ ውስተ፡ ሰማያት፡ በስብሐቲሁ፡ በሠረገላ፡ ብርሃን ወኢተፈለጥነ፡ እምኔሃ። ወይቤለነ፡ ንሥኡ፡ ዘንተ፡ አስማተ፡ ይኩንክሙ፡</incipit></msItem>
                      <msItem xml:id="ms_i1.5"><locus from="34v" to="42r" facs="039">Fols 34v–42r</locus><title>For Friday</title><incipit xml:lang="gez">በስመ፡ አብ፡ <gap reason="omitted"/> ይቀድሰነ፡ አስማቲሁ፡ ለክርስቶስ፡ ሲድላዊ፡ ቢድጋዊ፡ ብድሮፋ፡ ፈቃዲ፡ ገዳላኤል፡ መቃራሮ፡ በዝዚሐል፡ ገመለፈከኵል፡ ቄርሎካኤል፡። መኑ፡ አንተ፡ ብሩህ፡ አነ፡ ውእቱ፡</incipit></msItem>
                      <msItem xml:id="ms_i1.6"><locus from="42v" to="50r" facs="047">Fols 42v–50r</locus><title>For Saturday</title><incipit xml:lang="gez">በስመ፡ አብ፡ <gap reason="omitted"/> ጸሎተ፡ ሥርየት፡ እምነቶሙ፡ ለሐዋርያት፡ ወለኵሎሙ፡ ፸ወ፪ አርድዕት፡ ከማሁ፡ ይቤሎሙ፡ እግዚእ፡ ለአርዳኢሁ፡ አንትሙ፡ ውእቱ፡ አዕርክትየ፡</incipit></msItem>
                      <msItem xml:id="ms_i1.7"><locus from="50v" to="60r" facs="055">Fols 50v–60r</locus><title>For Sunday</title><incipit xml:lang="gez">በስመ፡ አብ፡ <gap reason="omitted"/> ብርሃናኤል፡ አጎዳ፡ ጽድቅ፡ አፍላላኤል፡ ዘንተ፡ አስማተ፡ ዘወሀቦሙ፡ እግዚአብሔር፡ ለአናንያ፡ ወአዛርያ፡ ወሚሳኤል፡</incipit></msItem>
                      <msItem xml:id="ms_i1.8"><locus from="60v" to="67v" facs="065">Fols 60v–67v</locus><title>Daily reading known as, “I beseech You lest I die early,” <foreign xml:lang="gez">ተማኅጸንኩ: ከመ: ኢይሙት: ዘእንበለ: ጊዜየ:</foreign></title><incipit xml:lang="gez">በስመ፡ አብ፡ <gap reason="omitted"/> ተማኅፀንኩ፡ ከመ፡ ኢይሙት፡ ዘእንበለ፡ ጊዜየ፡ ከመ፡ ሠራቂ፡ ሌሊት፡ ወከመ፡ ቀታሊ፡ መዓልት፡ ወሌሊት፡ በመንግሥተ፡ አብ፡</incipit></msItem>

                      <colophon xml:id="coloph1">
                        <locus target="#67v" facs="072">Fol. 67v</locus>
                        <q>“Written in the city of Mǝḥur, which is Gädamä Iyasus, from the creation of the world until now 7,409 (= 1909) in the reign of <persName ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/PRS7006Menilek">Mǝnilǝk</persName>, king of kings,
                        in the year of Mark the Evangelist, I Täklä Ṣǝyon have copied it. For ever and ever, Amen.”</q>
                      </colophon>
